Revision history for cif-router

v1.0.0-rc.5 2013-07
    - [security] fixed bug in authorized_write function

v1.0.0-rc.4 2013-07-10
    - misc bugfixes

0.99-RC3    2013-05
    - minor response fixes
    - throttling option for larger data-sets when someone wants to use the legacy api
    - json output cleanup
    - minor installation fixes

0.99.05 2012-10-31
    - added legacy json support module

0.99.04 2012-10-01
    - added query api restriction (eg: domain/malware, infrastructure/botnet, etc...)
    - merged in libcif
    - renamed REST driver to generic HTTP driver
    - fixed the write authorization

0.99.03 2012-07031
    - bugfixes
    - added submission interface
    - added key expiration check

0.99.02 2012-06-24
    - bugfixes, some re-factoring

0.99.01 2012-04-27
    - initial release
    - re-factored old CIF::WebAPI out to the CIF::Router::REST driver
